# 6. Multi-Stage Amplification Model

Unlike a single-stage drivetrain, VELOX X-22 introduces staged buffering.

---

## Stage 1

Power Capture

```text
Engine
   ↓
Input Coupler
```

---

## Stage 2

Pressure Generation

```text
Input Rotation
      ↓
Hydraulic Compression
```

---

## Stage 3

Storage

```text
Compression
      ↓
Pressure Core
```

---

## Stage 4

Synchronization

```text
Pressure
     ↓
Timing Logic
```

---

## Stage 5

Torque Injection

```text
Stored Energy
        ↓
Output Rotation
```

